-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

These modules implement the core features of the P.A.T.H. project.
At the moment there are two core modules: config.pm and hijack.pm.

The config.pm module is used to configure the scripts and to ensure that
every modules will be configured with the same parameters. It also offers
functions to check if an ip or mac address is valid.

All the hijacking stuff used in the P.A.T.H. project is placed in the 
hijack.pm module.

Everys module usage is descriped in the POD documentation of that module.

